# Ignore everything by default so unmanaged VS Code profile runtime files
# (e.g. state.json, window.json, cache dirs) are not accidentally committed.
*

# Allow git to descend into named profile subdirectories so the rules below
# can selectively un-ignore managed files within each profile.
!*/

# Un-ignore this file itself (the * above would otherwise match it) and the
# managed config files within each profile directory.
# Keep alphabetically sorted.
!.gitignore
!*/chatLanguageModels.json
!*/keybindings.json
!*/mcp.json
!*/prompts/
!*/prompts/**
!*/settings.json
!*/snippets/
!*/snippets/**
!*/tasks.json
